Response to Alex Hernandez<br><br>
Alex, you hereby take the reigh as keeper of the moral flame, one that I gladly give up. I do not attack your personal intergrity, in fact, I don't even recognize it. Give it a break Alex, this is just dialoge, this ain't you and me vs. Arnold in the Jungle ala Terminator after all. Why do you persist in over reaction and under reading?  Read previous posts, esp. those by &quot;tanker&quot;.  Chill out dude.<br>
So what that one person spit on you, I can count 100's, yes Alex, 100's of redneck right wingo patriot pro war folks who would have lynched me had they had the opportunity, that is before they got &quot;educated&quot; about the truth of Nam. Sadly, the truth usually ment that they lost a son, or rarely, a daughter (yes Alex, women served too).  Chill out.  I will never stop &quot;attacking&quot; you, or as I think of it, asking you to think, about the war.  Viet Nam maned our generation, spl.it into pieces that have yet come back together, more splinters than our parents ever could understand.  Alex, you got to get off your high horse and understand that there are many OTHER VICTIMS besides you.<br><br>
I ran from Nam, not to Canada, but to Europe, and stumbled into the 6 day war in Israel. Nothing to do with my great thinking, more like looking for hash.  I don't brag about those days and I am not ashamed about them either. I just got caught up in where it was at the time.  It is not relevant to us now.<br><br>
Alex, I have not had a full deck. let alone play with one since Tim Leary and I walked around Laguna Beach one day/year and discussed the way the sun danced with the moon...<br><br>
so you shot from the sky at targets that you never saw, with just a vest to hide behind, to I hear some guilt on your part, brave gunner?  Come on, down here, in the electronic ditches, I am willing to duke it out with you slugger. So, I suspect is Andy, aka Tanker, At least he forgives me for using a Mac.  For Christs Sakes Alex, get a grip and a sense of humor, or the back ward at your local V.A. hospital will gobble you up.   check you six, and don't get 5150'd.<br>
